- MAJOR: de Vrij et al. (Front Immunol, PMID 41798914, Feb 2026). NetMHCpan misses 20-70% of naturally presented peptides. Critical caveat for HLA/mimicry pipelines.
- MAJOR: Batignes et al. (Nat Comms, PMID 41776196, Mar 2026). AGS single-cell transcriptomics with SAMHD1 mutations. HIF-1alpha loss → metabolic shift → amplified IFN. HIF-1alpha stabilization reverses interferonopathy. SAMHD1 is our two-hit model gene.
